core.planner
Class Axiom

java.lang.Object
  core.planner.Axiom
All Implemented Interfaces:
Standardizable, java.lang.Cloneable
public final class Axiom
extends java.lang.Object
implements Standardizable, java.lang.Cloneable

The Axiom class implements a axiom. The class represents an axiom defined in the planning domain. The expected form is: (:- [n1] C1 [n2] C2 [n3] C3 ... [nn] Cn).
